channel.title: I need help naming the Cache file for a 718/742
channel.description: Hello! I need some help. I'm currently practicing coding a 742. I'm using the Rune-Evo source. As some of you may know, the cache goes and saves C:\Users\-user-\RuneEvo\evolution. I need help to change the cache downloading and saving as RuneEvo\Evolution.. So how do I set it to save those files as different names? When I made my attempt at this I got errors, so if anyone could point me in the right direction it'd be great!! <3 -Alex. :D
